Hello ios13! Helloo Human mode!! Hellooo interactive objects!!! Helloooo D efekt 3.0!!!! We have a huge update for you! We added lots of new features and updated the old ones. Now you can combine the effects with different shapes to create dazzling stories. Add text to your videos and make them react to the movement and sound. It sounds exciting isn t it We also added human mode which finds humans and applies effects only on them. Or the other way around! It s so much fun! We wanted to bring this feature to all of our users but because of hardware limitations it s only available from iPhone Xs and up.
